response.original_title: Giant Killers: The Story of the Lady Longhorns
response.overview: The story of Title IX's impact on the University of Texas, with a spotlight on its first director of women's athletics, Donna Lopiano; driven by the spirit of Title IX, Lopiano's legacy has paved the way for female athletes in Austin and beyond.
response.title: Giant Killers: The Story of the Lady Longhorns
